{
  "texts": [
    "Terrain slope (%) was estimated from the elevation data.",
    "Soil pH in water, soil texture (sand, silt, and clay, %), total organic C (TOC; %), total N (TN; %), and reference soil groups (World Reference Base, WRB) were obtained from the SoilGrids 2.0 database (Poggio et al., 2021).",
    "All spatial raster datasets were downloaded from the sources and used in the resolution of 5 arcmin.",
    "While it is possible to obtain the data in a finer resolution, the primary intent of the maps presented here is to parametrize and benchmark land surface models that simulate terrestrial vegetation.",
    "Thus, we opted to produce the maps in the resolution of 5 arcmin."
  ]
}